FRONTEND RULES
====================================

Framework:
- React (Vite)
- SPA only (React Router)
- CSS Modules or Styled Components only

Animations:
- Framer Motion for UI transitions
- GSAP + ScrollTrigger for scroll-based animations
- Lenis or Locomotive Scroll for smooth scrolling
- SVG-first animations (including 3D-style SVG)

Frontend Must Include:
- Sticky Navbar with scroll behavior
- Footer
- Hero section with animated 3D SVG centerpiece
- About section
- Rules section
- Registration section
- Event Timeline (scroll-synced)
- Teams section
- Organizers section
- Sponsors section
- Post-registration team dashboard

Design Rules:
- Dark, futuristic, premium robotics aesthetic
- High-contrast but accessible color palette
- Clean typography hierarchy
- Subtle hover micro-interactions
- Smooth inertia scrolling
- Scroll-triggered reveals, pinning, parallax

Forbidden:
- Emojis
- Over-animated gimmicks
- Heavy shaders
- Unstructured inline styles

====================================
ANIMATION SYSTEM RULES
====================================

You must design a reusable animation system.

Required modules:
- Smooth scroll provider
- Scroll reveal animations (fade, slide, scale)
- Parallax engine
- Section pinning logic
- SVG stroke and morph animations
- Hover micro-interactions
- Page transition animations

Implementation Rules:
- GSAP ScrollTrigger + Framer Motion
- Reusable hooks (e.g., useScrollAnimation, useParallax)
- Clean teardown on route change
- Performance-safe defaults
- SVG-first motion design

